381
00:34:12,346 --> 00:34:13,263
Dinamarquês.

382
00:34:13,388 --> 00:34:14,388
Tinha sotaque?

383
00:34:14,679 --> 00:34:16,554
Acho que ele era da Jutlândia.

384
00:34:16,596 --> 00:34:17,721
Certo, já deu.

385
00:34:18,471 --> 00:34:19,429
